01:04:42,596 --> 01:04:44,596
そしてそれ以外にも、ボイスパックがあります。
And besides that, there's also a voice pack.

827
01:04:44,596 --> 01:04:50,096
ここ数ヶ月ボイスパックを出していなかったので、ぜひ手に入れてくださいね。激レアです！
I haven't been doing any voice packs these past months, so make sure to get this one. Rare!

828
01:04:51,096 --> 01:04:54,596
そのほかには、久しぶりにボイスもあります。
Other than that, there's also a voice pack after a long time.

829
01:04:54,596 --> 01:04:59,096
最近あんまり参加してないので、ぜひこの機会に、おねがいします！
I haven't done many lately, so please take this opportunity!

830
01:05:00,704 --> 01:05:05,204
If you get the full set, then you receive a Polaroid from me alongside it,

831
01:05:05,204 --> 01:05:09,604
and if you're lucky to get the limited one, then it will be signed by my own hands!

832
01:05:09,904 --> 01:05:14,704
もちろん、いつも通りフルセットゲットすると、えー、チェキ、ついてきます！
Of course, as usual, if you get the full set, a Polaroid-style photo card comes with it!

